<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/crop.14.15.448.448.180/a8bfee30ly8h8w71x1lgbj20d50d5mxt.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1712717592&amp;ssig=Z6uKMKytU2</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:55:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>1</ttl><item><title>喝粥养胃？真的吗？其实，粥真没这么健康。🤦🏻♂️①大米等淀粉类食物在烹煮过程中会出现“糊化效应”，幼儿、高龄老人更易消化、吸收。但对于普通人而言，...</title><description>喝粥养胃？真的吗？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;其实，粥真没这么健康。🤦🏻♂️&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;①大米等淀粉类食物在烹煮过程中会出现“糊化效应”，幼儿、高龄老人更易消化、吸收。但对于普通人而言，长期进食过于软烂的食物，甚至会出现消化功能衰退；&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;②本身患有胃酸分泌过多、胃食管反流、溃疡和胃穿孔的人，喝粥容易加重胃酸分泌，加重病情；&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;③受糊化效应的影响，粥类的升糖指数更高，并不适合控制血糖；&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;④粥中营养仅以碳水化合物为主，长期喝粥，会导致其他营养素缺乏。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%998%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%BB%E8%83%83%E8%B0%A3%E8%A8%80%E8%BF%9F%E6%97%A9%E6%8A%8A%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%83%83%